@SG_ML_HEADER_sg_detaileddescription Detailed Description
@SG_ML_L01301FSGXFileBinUtilities../cppclass/sgxfilebinutilities provides access to the file bin builtin to SGEXTN. Deleted user data should be moved to the file bin so that it can be recovered if the user changes their mind. Files in the bin are automatically deleted after a period of time. Files in the bin must be accessed through their @SG_ML_L00D019SGXIdentifier../cppclass/sgxidentifier, not through the path.
@SG_ML_BLANKLINE
