Move the file at file path @SG_ML_B001s to the file bin. This returns -2 if a file system error caused the operation to fail, 0 if there is no file at @SG_ML_B001s, and 1 if the operation is successful.
@SG_ML_NOTE The original path of the file is stored in the file bin after its deletion and can be used for recovery of deleted files.
@SG_ML_NOTE Do not move application generated files to the bin, instead delete them directly using @SG_ML_L02204DSGXFileSystem::permanentDeleteFile../cppclass/sgxfilesystem#static_int_permanentDeleteFile_const_SGXString_ref_. The file bin is only for user data.
